title: MICKEY_MOUSE
about_story: Mickey taught us, To laugh at yourself,is to love yourself

page_content: 'Oh,Toodles!','Let's roll' Do u guys really remember these lines? Ofc,that's our mickey.
It brings back to our nostalia,a truly loved cartoon its not just a show but an emotion,a beautiful one.
A cheerful and mischievous character of all the time.
